# CS2 Server Picker Linux - Todo List

# Base Api: https://api.steampowered.com/ISteamApps/GetSDRConfig/v1/?appid=730

## Core Features
- [ ] Get server list from the API
- [ ] Get ip and port from the server list
- [ ] Get server details
- [ ] User interface for displaying server list
- [ ] Button for refreshing, block all, unblock all
- [ ] Button for block selected
- [ ] Use iptable to temporarily block servers 

